Testovano na Linux Ubuntu 18.04.4 LTS

Pro beh je potreba mit nainstalovany python3.6 a pip
    sudo apt-get update
    apt-get install python3-pip

Nainstalujeme selenium a beahve
    pip3 install selenium
    pip3 install behave
    sudo apt install python3-behave

Dale je potreba zpristupnit webdriver pro ovladani prohlizece (pro Firefox to je geckodriver dostupny z: https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases), po stahnuti je potreba jej umistit do adresare /usr/local/bin a zmenit prava pres chmod +x, driver pouzity pri testovani je umisten v adresari ./drivers.
    sudo cp /drivers/geckodriver /usr/local/bin

Nainstalovat GNU AWK (pro kompatibilitu s generovanymi skripty)
    sudo apt-get update
    sudo apt-get install gawk

Spusteni: behave
Debug: behave -n "nazev scenare" --no-capture -f plain
